UID:81993a2bdfd010b2855dfb371de93755@family-events-agent
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:storytime,library,baby,toddler,reading
DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Chicago Public Library\\nCost: free\\nAges: 0-60 mo
 nths\\nCategory: Film & Events\\n\\nJoin us for a screening of When Harry 
 Met Sally\, directed by the late Rob Reiner . Meg Ryan and Billy Crystal s
 tar as two best friends of the opposite sex in the blockbuster\, heartwarm
 ing romantic comedy When Harry Met Sally. Harry Burns and Sally Albright m
 eet when the share a car on a trip from Chicago to New York right after bo
