CATEGORIES:storytime,library,baby,toddler,reading
DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Chicago Public Library\\nCost: free\\nAges: 0-18 mo
 nths\\nCategory: Storytime\\n\\nJoin our children's librarians for this sp
 ecial 25-minute story time for babies and their caregivers. We’ll share 
 songs\, rhymes and books while helping to build baby’s early literacy an
 d social-emotional skills. For children birth to 18 months and their careg
